  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个状态图，描述课堂服务里的内容采集流程。核心是从Education_ContentCDN拉流，然后有个累积状态，攒够一定节拍数再输出。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "ACCUMULATE",
        "OUTPUT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。所以起点是ContentCDN，然后进入一个叫ACCUMULATE的状态。这个累积的终止条件是什么？是固定数量还是时间触发？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ACCUMULATE",
        "beat",
        "RATIO"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "用beat计数。当beat小于RATIO减1的时候，继续留在ACCUMULATE状态自循环；当beat等于RATIO减1，或者到了最后一包，就转到OUTPUT状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "beat",
        "RATIO",
        "LAST",
        "OUTPUT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画好了状态转移：ACCUMULATE自循环标注beat < RATIO-1，到OUTPUT的转移标注beat == RATIO-1 or LAST。那OUTPUT之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ACCUMULATE",
        "OUTPUT",
        "beat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "OUTPUT输出完之后要回到ACCUMULATE继续采集。条件是m_ready，表示输出模块就绪了。另外需要在两个状态旁边加注释说明：ACCUMULATE是窄节拍收集到buffer，OUTPUT是buffer满了输出宽节拍。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OUTPUT",
        "ACCUMULATE",
        "m_ready",
        "buffer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：OUTPUT通过m_ready回到ACCUMULATE，形成循环。右侧注释分别说明buffer的收集和输出。图标题用stateDiagram-v2，整体叫Education_ClassroomService对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "stateDiagram-v2",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "m_ready"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "标题格式不对，应该是%%{Education_ClassroomService}%%这种指令形式，不是普通的标题。还有RATIO和LAST这些常量需要明确是逻辑判断条件。",
      "elements_involved": [
